         MNOTE *,'Including IEZCIB mapping macro'                       00800000
.*                                                                      00810000
.* IEZCIB does not generate a DSECT-statement                           00820000
CIB      DSECT ,                       * Start of CIB DSECT             00830000
         IEZCIB ,                      *                                00840000
         EQUOVR *END                                                    00850000
*                                                                       00860000
CIB      DSECT ,                       * Resume CIB DSECT               00870000
         ORG                                                            00880000
*                                                                       00890000
* Length of CIB is contained in field CIBLEN (1 byte) in units          00900000
* of doublewords, therefore no length equate is supplied.               00910000
*                                                                       00920000
* CIBHDR is defined as the fixed part of the CIB i.e. the CIB without   00930000
* the CIBDATA field.                                                    00940000
*                                                                       00950000
CIBHDR   EQU   CIB                     *                                00960000
CIBHDR_LEN EQU CIBDATA-CIBHDR          *                                00970000
*                                                                       00980000
CIBX     DSECT ,                       * Resume CIB extension           00990000
         ORG                                                            01000000
CIBX_LEN EQU   *-CIBX                  * Length of CIB extension        01010000
